Iosevka-core (reduced Iosevka font set)

Iosevka-core provides a reduced installation of the Iosevka monospace
font family, intended for common use cases such as terminals, text
editors, and lightweight graphical applications.

Only the following TTC files are installed:
  - Iosevka-Regular.ttc
  - Iosevka-Bold.ttc

Because these are TrueType Collections, they include the Iosevka,
Iosevka Term, and Iosevka Fixed families (Regular, Bold, Italic, and
Bold Italic styles for each). Iosevka Term is the terminal-optimized
spacing and works well in terminals and lightweight window managers
(Fluxbox, dwm, Openbox, etc.).

Only 2 of the 9 upstream weight collections are installed; the other
weights (Thin, Light, Medium, SemiBold, Heavy, etc.) are intentionally
omitted to reduce disk usage from ~400 MB to ~100 MB.

WARNING
-------
This package conflicts with the full "Iosevka" package available at:

  https://slackbuilds.org/repository/15.0/system/Iosevka/

Both packages install files with the same names. Only one of them
should be installed at a time.
